# Why LCM?

Suppose cycle lengths are

```
4

6
```

Cycle 1 repeats every

```
4
```

Cycle 2 repeats every

```
6
```

Need first common time

```
4

8

12  ✓
```

```
6

12 ✓
```

Hence

```
LCM(4,6)=12
```

